 GNOME Desktop 
    Alt+Tab       Switch among tasks
    Ctrl+PgUp     Switch among terminal, Left
    Ctrl+PgDn     Switch among terminal, Right
    Ctrl+Alt+->   Move to Right Virtual Desktop
    Ctrl+Alt+<-   Move to Left Virtual Desktop
    Shift+PgUp    Browse terminal display
    Shift+PgDn    ......................

Python3 venv
    temporarily adding "/..../python/anaconda3/bin/" to $PATH
    > cd bin
    > python3 -m venv py3venv
    > source ~/bin/py3venv/bin/activate.csh     ## entering into venv of Python3
    > python --version
    Python 3.7.4
    > deactive                                  ## exit venv
    
